posting_body: ['Eastlake Studio - 2 Weeks Free', 'Property Address', '261 E Boston St - 4 | Seattle, WA 98102', 'Available: 07/30/2022', 'Offered By', 'Seattle Property Management Assoc, LLC', 'Description', 'The Boston is located just off Eastlake Ave and is within walking distance to a variety of nearby shops and restaurants including Serafina, Grand Central Bakery and Haymaker.', 'Terry Pettus Park is a small public park on Lake Union which is easily accessed off Fairview Ave and a great spot to dip your toes in to cool off on a hot summers day.', 'This cozy basement studio has an efficient kitchen layout which includes a dishwasher and a full size refrigerator.', 'There is an in-unit washer dryer stack.', ' We are offering this studio apartment at $1095 per month plus a $50 utility fee', 'At the time of application we require payment of the $25 application fee per person and a $1000 deposit that is then applied to the refundable security deposit upon approval.', 'This building is non-smoking.', 'Cats are allowed.', 'sorry, no dogs.', 'If you would like more information or to schedule a tour, please contact Ryan at', 'show contact info', 'Amenities', 'Small Building', 'Laundry in-unit', 'near transportation', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1.0BA', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,095.00', 'Available: 07/30/2022', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,000.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
